      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>newPrice</span>\" => <span class=sf-dump-num>1199.0</span>
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>category</span>\" => <span class=sf-dump-note>array:6</span> [ &#8230;6]
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>brand</span>\" => <span class=sf-dump-note>array:6</span> [ &#8230;6]
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>date</span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"16 characters\">24th March, 2026</span>\"
    </samp>]
    <span class=sf-dump-index>2</span> => <span class=sf-dump-note>array:11</span> [<samp data-depth=3 class=sf-dump-compact>
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>id</span>\" => <span class=sf-dump-num>1</span>
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>title</span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"48 characters\">TCL 85&quot; Q Series QLED 4K UHD HDR Smart Google TV</span>\"
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>slug</span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"47 characters\">tcl-85-q-series-qled-4k-uhd-hdr-smart-google-tv</span>\"
      \"<span class=sf-dump-key>description</span>\" => \"\"\"
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3905 characters\">&lt;p&gt;Step Up to QLED &amp;mdash; Better Color, Better Picture, Better Value. Upgrade from ordinary 4K to extraordinary QLED. The TCL Q51K QLED 4K Smart TV delivers over a billion brilliant colors, striking brightness, and lifelike clarity powered by Quantum Dot technology. From family movie nights to intense gaming sessions, it&amp;rsquo;s exceptional performance at an exceptional price. TCL Q51K Series Smart TVs combine premium picture technology with outstanding value for endless entertainment. HDR PRO+ with Dolby Vision lets you enjoy enhanced contrast, accurate colors and fine details utilizing all the most advanced HDR formats. Motion Rate 240 with MEMC frame insertion provides exceptional motion clarity. TCL&amp;rsquo;s High Brightness Direct LED Backlight produces brighter images for an enhanced viewing experience for all your favorite movies and TV shows. Now featuring the TCL AIPQ Processor that optimizes each scene for an unrivaled cinematic experience. Experience the latest sound technologies with Dolby Atmos. TCL Q51K Series Smart TVs: a Smart Value 4K QLED TV.&lt;/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3905 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3905 characters\">&lt;ul&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3905 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;QLED Quantum Dot Color&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;ndash; Experience over a billion vibrant shades for richer, more realistic color. From vivid sunsets to fast-paced sports, QLED delivers a picture that pops compared with basic LED TVs. Perfect for movie lovers, sports fans, and anyone who wants color that feels real.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3905 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;High Brightness LED Backlight&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;ndash; Brighter highlights, bolder contrast, and crisp detail&amp;mdash;even in bright rooms or daytime viewing. Perfect for open-concept living rooms or sunny family spaces.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3905 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HDR PRO+ with Dolby Vision, HDR10+, and HLG&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;ndash; Enjoy cinematic contrast and accurate color with every frame thanks to today&amp;rsquo;s most advanced HDR formats. Perfect for streaming blockbusters or HDR content from Netflix, Disney+, and Prime Video.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3905 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TCL AIPQ Processor&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;ndash; The smart AIPQ Engine analyzes content in real time to optimize brightness, contrast, and color&amp;mdash;so everything you watch looks incredible. Perfect for binge-watchers who want consistent quality across every show.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3905 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dolby Atmos + DTS Virtual:X Audio&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;ndash; Immerse yourself in 3D sound that fills your space. Every voice, soundtrack, and explosion sounds rich and natural&amp;mdash;no soundbar required. Perfect for family movie nights and gamers who want theater-like audio.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3905 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Auto Game Mode (ALLM)&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;ndash; Automatically switches to low-latency mode for smoother, faster gameplay and instant on-screen response. Perfect for gamers who demand lightning-fast action with no lag.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3905 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Google TV with Voice Remote&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;ndash; All your favorite apps, shows, and live channels in one easy-to-use interface&amp;mdash;now with simple voice control. Just say it to find it: &amp;ldquo;Play Ted Lasso&amp;rdquo; or &amp;ldquo;Open YouTube.&amp;rdquo; Built-in Chromecast makes sharing from your phone instant. Perfect for busy families and anyone who wants hands-free control and streaming simplicity.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3905 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TCL TV+ Free Streaming&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;ndash; Discover over 350 free live channels and thousands of on-demand movies and shows&amp;mdash;no subscriptions or logins required. TCL TV+ puts endless entertainment at your fingertips right out of the box. Perfect for cord-cutters and families who want instant, free entertainment value.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3905 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Better Color. Better Picture. Better Value. Only with TCL&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;ndash; QLED delivers brighter visuals, richer color, and better contrast than traditional LED or standard UHD. With the TCL Q51K, you&amp;rsquo;re not just watching TV &amp;mdash; you&amp;rsquo;re experiencing more life in every pixel. It&amp;rsquo;s the smarter upgrade for families, gamers, and everyday entertainment.&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
        <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3905 characters\">&lt;/ul&gt;</span>
        \"\"\"
